episodes.title: GAME OVER! KOGGC Cult Leader David E. Taylor Face to Face With Human Trafficking Charges!
episodes.description:
Welcome to Full Frontal Investigation, a bold and unapologetic non-Christian YouTube channel dedicated to exposing the dark underbelly of religious cults, corrupt churches, YouTube “prophets,” and the vast web of financial and criminal misconduct that hides behind the veil of faith in America.

This channel was created out of a deep need for truth, accountability, and justice—especially in spaces that often operate beyond the reach of scrutiny.

While religion should be a source of comfort, guidance, and community, it has also been exploited by con artists, narcissists, and criminal enterprises that use scripture as a smokescreen and manipulate faith for power and profit.

Our mission is clear: Shine an unflinching light on religious corruption, financial exploitation, and the cults that prey on the vulnerable.

1. Religious Cults in America from secretive compounds to live-streamed sermons, we dissect the mechanics of control, manipulation, and abuse employed by modern-day cult leaders. Whether it’s a fringe sect in the desert or a mega-church with millions of followers, we explore how these organizations isolate followers, suppress dissent, and enforce obedience—sometimes with devastating consequences.

2. Financial Fraud and Criminal Activity: Behind many charismatic leaders lies a paper trail of deceit. We dig deep into IRS filings, court records, real estate transactions, and whistleblower testimonies to uncover the financial schemes that funnel millions into the pockets of “spiritual leaders.” From Ponzi schemes disguised as “blessings” to money laundering masked as ministry work, we follow the money—and it often leads to disturbing revelations.

3. Mortgage and Real Estate Scams: Religious organizations frequently engage in shady real estate ventures—buying properties under shell companies, flipping churches for profit, or coercing followers to sign over deeds to their homes in exchange for promises of divine favor. Full Frontal Investigation highlights the systemic abuse of nonprofit status and investigates how some churches operate like real estate conglomerates rather than places of worship.

4. YouTube Prophets and Digital Cult Leaders: A new breed of self-proclaimed “prophets” is emerging online—gathering massive audiences, donations, and power through social media. With prophetic livestreams, donation links, and apocalyptic warnings, these digital influencers claim to speak for God while raking in tens of thousands of dollars. We analyze their tactics, fact-check their prophecies, and investigate where the money really goes.

5. Abuse of Nonprofit Religious Status: Churches enjoy unique legal protections and tax exemptions in the United States. This loophole has created fertile ground for financial exploitation. We spotlight how certain ministries, and religious figures abuse this status to hide assets, avoid taxes, and escape accountability.

Religion is one of the most powerful forces in human history. At its best, it inspires compassion, community, and purpose. At its worst, it becomes a tool of psychological coercion, financial exploitation, and criminal behavior—all under the protection of spiritual authority.

In the United States, religious organizations are rarely held accountable. Their financials are largely exempt from transparency laws. Their leaders are elevated to untouchable status. And their followers are often too afraid—or too conditioned—to speak out.
That’s where Full-Frontal Investigation comes in.
We’re not anti-religion. We’re anti-corruption.
This channel is a voice for the voiceless. A digital watchdog that refuses to look away. A platform where truth outweighs doctrine, and justice speaks louder than false prophecy.

Our viewers come from all walks of life—former cult members, spiritual seekers, journalists, legal experts, and people who simply care about truth and accountability. If you’ve ever questioned a religious leader’s motives, wondered where your donation really went, or watched a “prophet” make wild predictions with no consequences—you’re in the right place.
We encourage respectful discussion, open inquiry, and evidence-based debate. We welcome whistleblowers, survivors, and investigators to reach out and share what they know.

If you're tired of watching fraud flourish behind pulpits…
If you believe faith should never be used as a weapon for control…
If you want to be part of a movement holding these institutions accountable…

Turn on notifications. Watch. Share. See something. Say Something!

We take anonymity seriously. If you have credible information, documents, or stories to share, please contact us securely at (314)492-3356 We vet all sources, protect whistleblower identities, and strive to maintain the highest journalistic standards.

Welcome to Full Frontal Investigation, the YouTube channel that dares to uncover the truths too many are afraid to tell. In an age where mega-churches operate more like multi-million dollar corporations than places of worship, we ask the questions others won’t—and follow the paper trails they try to hide. With hard-hitting research, source-backed exposés, and a relentless pursuit of accountability, Full Frontal Investigation is where transparency meets fearless journalism.

Our mission is simple but vital: to expose the misuse of faith, money, and influence in the world of organized religion. We're not here to challenge belief—we're here to challenge corruption.

🎥 What We Investigate
Full Frontal Investigation is a deep-dive channel committed to pulling back the curtain on some of the most scandalous and underreported activities taking place within religious institutions—especially the growing number of mega-churches that use religion to mask empire-building.

Our investigations focus on:

Religious Fraud: From fake miracles and prophetic manipulation to cult-like control tactics, we expose how some spiritual leaders prey on vulnerability and emotion to gain power and wealth.

Tax Evasion & Financial Loopholes: Churches in the U.S. enjoy unique tax-exempt status, and many exploit that to operate private businesses, launder money, or hoard personal wealth—often at the expense of their congregants and communities.
Mortgage & Real Estate Fraud: We uncover how some mega-churches build vast real estate portfolios, secure shady loans, and hide assets behind shell corporations—all under the guise of “expanding the ministry.”

Lavish Lifestyles Funded by Tithes: Gulfstreams, Bentleys, mansions, and designer wardrobes—our channel exposes how some church leaders use donations meant for charity and ministry to bankroll opulent lives that resemble that of celebrities, not servants of the people.

Cult Tactics & Psychological Manipulation: Many religious organizations use guilt, shame, isolation, and control to keep members compliant. We highlight patterns that indicate spiritual abuse and cult behavior masked as faith.
🔍 How We Work
We rely on:

Leaked documents from insiders
Tax records and 990 forms (when applicable)
Real estate databases and mortgage history
Court filings, bankruptcy records, and criminal complaints
Whistleblower interviews and ex-member testimonials
Open-source intelligence (OSINT) and financial data mining
Publicly available sermons, livestreams, and social media
Each episode is meticulously researched and fact-checked. We back our claims with documentation, visual receipts, and data analysis. We believe truth matters—and that evidence is the best defense against misinformation.

⚖️ Why This Matters
Religious freedom is a cornerstone of many societies, but freedom does not mean immunity from scrutiny. When tax-exempt organizations commit fraud, they’re not only breaking the law—they’re exploiting the trust of millions.

Our investigations shine light into dark corners where accountability has long been absent. By holding powerful institutions to the same standards as everyone else, we advocate for:

Financial transparency
Legal and ethical oversight
Protection for whistleblowers and victims
Restoration of public trust in legitimate faith-based institutions
We’re not anti-religion. We’re anti-corruption.

📺 Must-Watch Series
1. Pastor Profiles: Deep dives into the lives, finances, and controversies of well-known church leaders.
2. The Real Estate Empire Files: Following the money into commercial ventures, undeclared assets, and real estate schemes.
3. Faith or Fraud?: Dissecting viral miracles, staged healings, and other manipulative tactics.
4. Church Crimes & Court Cases: Covering ongoing legal battles involving church institutions, including fraud charges, sexual misconduct, and racketeering.
5. The Money Behind the Ministry: Investigating donation funnels, nonprofit fraud, and multimillion-dollar ministry brands.

💬 Join the Investigation
At Full Frontal Investigation, we believe truth thrives in community. Our viewers often bring crucial tips, leads, and context that help push investigations further. Whether you're an ex-member, an insider, or a curious citizen, your voice matters.

You can submit information confidentially, and we take protection of sources seriously.

👉 Got a tip? Email us securely alexstravonovich@gmail.com

👉 Want to join the movement? Like, comment, and subscribe. The algorithm may try to silence uncomfortable truths—but your engagement helps us stay seen.

🔥 Our Values
Integrity over influence
Truth over tradition
Courage over comfort
We’re here to disturb the status quo, to shine a spotlight where few dare to look, and to empower the public with information that institutions would rather keep buried. 

Welcome to Full Frontal Investigation.
Because when faith becomes a business, someone has to follow the money
